{
  "id": "adv_event_2603_01_02",
  "title": "歌うように",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-evening",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "この楽譜に描かれた絵とかメッセージはね\n全部、お姉ちゃんが私のために書いてくれたものなんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 8.1773015022,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "幼少期の麻奈様直筆！？\nそ、そんな貴重な品に触れてしまったなんて……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.2333333333,
      "endTime": 15.3444221179,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-evening",
      "startTime": 8.3839683215
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-evening",
      "startTime": 15.5444220225
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ。その楽譜、もとは私のだし気にしなくて大丈夫よ\nリビングに楽器が沢山あったでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.5444220225,
      "endTime": 25.2347170512,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-evening",
      "startTime": 25.4480504036
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、アップライトピアノからヴァイオリン……\nスレイベルにフルートまで、豊富にありましたわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.4480504036,
      "endTime": 33.370203209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-evening",
      "startTime": 33.5702030183
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "お父さんとお母さんの仕事道具なんだけど\n子供の頃、私とお姉ちゃんはあれでよく遊んでたのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.5702030183,
      "endTime": 40.8573007586,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "そしたらある日、お母さんが「ピアノを教えてあげる」\nって言ってくれて……お姉ちゃん、はしゃいでたなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.0706341109,
      "endTime": 50.7270737014,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-evening",
      "startTime": 50.9337402346
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "でも私はピアノよりもトライアングルやカスタネットの\n方が楽しくて。すぐにはピアノに興味が持てなかったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.9337402346,
      "endTime": 60.1615861895,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-evening",
      "startTime": 60.3615861895
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、琴乃がトライアングルを演奏している姿を\n想像したら、なんだか可愛くて微笑ましいですわねぇ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.3615861895,
      "endTime": 69.3033546451,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-evening",
      "startTime": 69.4966879211
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "それ、お姉ちゃんにも言われた気がする。お姉ちゃんと\n一緒に歌ったり演奏したり。あの時間、大好きだったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.4966879211,
      "endTime": 81.4831732116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈様と仲睦まじく過ごしていたのですね\n聞いてるだけで頬が緩んでしまいますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.4666669846,
      "endTime": 89.5000003179,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-evening",
      "startTime": 81.6831732116
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "ですが、発表会に出るまでピアノの腕が上達するなんて\n琴乃は飲み込みが早かったんですのねぇ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.3666636786,
      "endTime": 97.90298891100001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-evening",
      "startTime": 89.6977746013
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-evening",
      "startTime": 98.1163222634
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、そういう訳でもなくて……お姉ちゃんがある日\n突然「一緒に発表会に出よう！」って誘ってくれたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.1163222634,
      "endTime": 109.6312651955,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "最初は嫌だったわ。片手でしか弾けなくて、人前で発表\nなんて出来る腕前じゃなかったし。何より恥ずかしくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.8379317287,
      "endTime": 120.0055960659,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-evening",
      "startTime": 120.2055960659
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "でもお姉ちゃんがね「琴乃と演奏したい」って\n言ってくれたのが嬉しくて一気にやる気が湧いてきたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.2055960659,
      "endTime": 127.7715596203,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-evening",
      "startTime": 128.8648928964
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "でも練習を始めても、まだ小学校に上がったばかりの\n私には難しくて、何度も投げ出しそうになって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.9315600717,
      "endTime": 138.38112958309998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-evening",
      "startTime": 138.5811293924
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "そうしたらお姉ちゃんが\n「楽譜に魔法をかけてあげる！」って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.5811293924,
      "endTime": 143.72802270289998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-evening",
      "startTime": 144.8746887847
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "それが、この楽譜の可愛い絵とメッセージ……\n琴乃の興味を引くために描いてくれたんですのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.9080231353,
      "endTime": 155.5797463103,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-evening",
      "startTime": 155.7930796627
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "うん、お姉ちゃんのおかげで、楽譜を開くのが\n楽しくなって、どんどんピアノが好きになっていったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.7930796627,
      "endTime": 164.0083404545,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-evening",
      "startTime": 164.2016737306
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "お母さんがいない時も、私が弾けるようになるまで\nお姉ちゃんが丁寧に教えてくれて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.2016737306,
      "endTime": 170.4425125445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "さすが麻奈様ですわ！\nピアノもお上手だったなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.2666669846,
      "endTime": 176.2000003179,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-evening",
      "startTime": 170.6425126398
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-evening",
      "startTime": 176.4684980715
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、大きくなってからお母さんに聞いたんだけど\n実はお姉ちゃんも苦手だったらしいの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.4684980715,
      "endTime": 184.7522851312,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-evening",
      "startTime": 184.9456182167
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_02-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "ええぇ！？\nでも琴乃に教えてくれていたんですわよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.9456182167,
      "endTime": 189.84595858309999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-evening",
      "startTime": 190.0459585831
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
